    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "Through Rose-Coloured Glasses",
        "Description": "Evelyn Crane&apos;s motto has always been &quot;stop and smell the flowers&quot;, but lately she has been struggling to look on the bright side. Her budding romance with the married Mr. Rose ended in heartbreak when the illicit affair was exposed by Mr. Dennell. Peering through the steamed glass of the greenhouse, he caught them in the act, and after blackmailing them, he revealed the truth to Mrs. Rose anyway, for a further price.\rThe scorned wife sees her husband&apos;s true colours now and is out for revenge.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as magicdave94.",
